      "id": "m9e5j9j4",
      "questionNumber": 9,
      "questionText": "<p>Which of the following amine (s) show (s) positive carbylamine test?</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m9gwxeom/8265460d-9971-4a12-9978-e6b9ab018322/a993a360-1918-11f0-b368-fb15543a0775/file-jaoe38c1m9gwxeon.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m9gwxeom/8265460d-9971-4a12-9978-e6b9ab018322/a993a360-1918-11f0-b368-fb15543a0775/file-jaoe38c1m9gwxeon.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"JEE Main 2025 (Online) 7th April Morning Shift Chemistry - Compounds Containing Nitrogen Question 31 English 1\"></p>\n<p>B. $\\left(\\mathrm{CH}_3\\right)_2 \\mathrm{NH}$</p>\n<p>C. $\\mathrm{CH}_3 \\mathrm{NH}_2$</p>\n<p>D. $\\left(\\mathrm{CH}_3\\right)_3 \\mathrm{~N}$</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m9gwykzp/870b3555-23b5-4028-be8f-b7142cbf50ea/ca422f50-1918-11f0-b368-fb15543a0775/file-jaoe38c1m9gwykzq.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m9gwykzp/870b3555-23b5-4028-be8f-b7142cbf50ea/ca422f50-1918-11f0-b368-fb15543a0775/file-jaoe38c1m9gwykzq.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"JEE Main 2025 (Online) 7th April Morning Shift Chemistry - Compounds Containing Nitrogen Question 31 English 2\"></p>\n<p>Choose the correct answer from the options given below:</p>",
      "options": [
        " C Only\n",
        " B, C and D Only\n",
        " A and E Only\n",
        " A and C Only"
